seller.description:
Hello,
I'm Zafar, and professional CGI Artist and video creator. 

I have provided services in Motion graphics, 2D animation, Rotoscoping, Chromakeying with 3D Modeling, Animating, Texturing, Rigging, and Video editing, also I have provided Adobe After Effects Services. 

I'm using AutoDesk Maya, Substance Painter, Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, Premiere Pro, and many more. Please see my profile and judge me. Please feel free to contact me any time, I'm always excited about the new project! 

Regards, 
Zafar Iqbal
